data.description: Welcome to this dream home located in the serene community Oak Villages of Sugarmill Woods!!  This meticulously maintained home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, a spacious 2294 living square feet and a gorgeous salt water pool. As soon as you pull into the driveway, you'll be greeted by a beautifully landscaped front yard and a 2-car attached garage. Step inside this immaculate home and be amazed by the modern updates and upgrades throughout.  The kitchen features all brand new appliances 2022/2023 and overlooks a large family room perfect for whipping up delicious meals while entertaining with family and friends.  New features installed in 2023 include HVAC UV air purifier, pool pump, pool light, all new Bahia sod, sprinkler system.  Installed in 2021 include a new roof w/solar powered attic vents, hot water heater, garage door, entrance door, back door, gutter guards, shower door.  All new lighting & ceiling fans throughout, window blinds, HVAC under contract and serviced every 6 months and pest prevention every 3 months and much, much more.  Spend your day lounging by the pool soaking up the Florida sun.  This home boast love and care;  privacy and convenience;  low Hoa’s, No Flood, No Cdd’s.  Easy access to all major road ways, shopping, dining, and entertainment options, as well as top-rated schools.  Book your showing today!!!
